37195>>>>>    Function SetUserPassword String sLoginName String sPassword Returns Boolean
37197>>>>>        Handle hoUserDD
37197>>>>>        Integer iErr
37197>>>>>        Get phoUserDD to hoUserDD
37198>>>>>        
37198>>>>>        //  Find the user
37198>>>>>        Send Clear of hoUserDD
37199>>>>>        Move sLoginName to WebAppUser.LoginName
37200>>>>>        Send Find of hoUserDD EQ Index.1
37201>>>>>        If (not(Found)) Begin
37203>>>>>            Send Clear of hoUserDD
37204>>>>>            Function_Return False
37205>>>>>        End
37205>>>>>>
37205>>>>>        
37205>>>>>        If (not(CreatePasswordHash(Self, Trim(sPassword), &sPassword))) Begin
37207>>>>>            Send Clear of hoUserDD
37208>>>>>            Function_Return False
37209>>>>>        End
37209>>>>>>
37209>>>>>        Set Field_Changed_Value of hoUserDD Field WebAppUser.Password to sPassword
37210>>>>>        Get Request_Validate of hoUserDD to iErr
37211>>>>>        If (iErr) Begin
37213>>>>>            Send Clear of hoUserDD
37214>>>>>            Function_Return False
37215>>>>>        End
37215>>>>>>
37215>>>>>        
37215>>>>>        Send Request_Save of hoUserDD
37216>>>>>        Function_Return (not(Err))
