37229>>>>>    //
37229>>>>>    // This procedure is called when validating a session and after logging in. Its purpose is to 
37229>>>>>    // update properties based on the session and user data. Augment this function to update 
37229>>>>>    // properties based on the session / user table. Note that WebAppUser and WebAppSession contain
37229>>>>>    // the right records when this procedure is called.
37229>>>>>    //
37229>>>>>    // Params:
37229>>>>>    //      bClear   True if the procedure is called before session validation to clear properties.
37229>>>>>    //
37229>>>>>    Procedure UpdateSessionProperties Boolean bClear
37231>>>>>        Handle hoUserDD
37231>>>>>        
37231>>>>>        Get phoUserDD to hoUserDD
37232>>>>>        
37232>>>>>        //  Update user properties
37232>>>>>        If (not(bClear) and HasRecord(hoUserDD)) Begin
37234>>>>>            Set psUsername to (Trim(WebAppUser.FullName))
37235>>>>>            Set psLoginName to (Trim(WebAppUser.LoginName))
37236>>>>>            Set piUserRights to WebAppUser.Rights
37237>>>>>            
37237>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesSet 
37238>>>>>        End
37238>>>>>>
37238>>>>>        Else Begin
37239>>>>>            Set psUsername to ""
37240>>>>>            Set psLoginName to ""
37241>>>>>            Set piUserRights to 0
37242>>>>>            
37242>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesClear
37243>>>>>        End
37243>>>>>>
37243>>>>>    End_Procedure
37244>>>>>    
37244>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesSet
37246>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37246>>>>>    End_Procedure
37247>>>>>    
37247>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesClear
37249>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37249>>>>>    End_Procedure
