37250>>>>>    Procedure EndSession
37252>>>>>        Integer iErr
37252>>>>>        Boolean bLogWebSession
37252>>>>>        Handle hoSessionDD       
37252>>>>>        
37252>>>>>        Get phoSessionDD to hoSessionDD
37253>>>>>        Get pbLogWebSession to bLogWebSession
37254>>>>>        If not bLogWebSession Begin
37256>>>>>            Forward Send EndSession
37258>>>>>            Procedure_Return
37259>>>>>        End
37259>>>>>>
37259>>>>>            
37259>>>>>        //  Check if session exists
37259>>>>>        Send Clear of hoSessionDD
37260>>>>>        Get psSessionKey to WebAppSession.SessionKey
37261>>>>>        
37261>>>>>        Send Find of hoSessionDD EQ Index.1
37262>>>>>        If (Found) Begin
37264>>>>>            Set Field_Changed_Value of hoSessionDD Field WebAppSession.Active to "N"
37265>>>>>            Get Request_Validate of hoSessionDD to iErr
37266>>>>>            If (iErr) Begin
37268>>>>>                // this should not happen. If it does its a programming error
37268>>>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM C_$WebAppSessionValidateFailed
37269>>>>>>
37269>>>>>                Procedure_Return
37270>>>>>            End
37270>>>>>>
37270>>>>>            Send Request_Save of hoSessionDD
37271>>>>>        End
37271>>>>>>
37271>>>>>    End_Procedure
